		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Okay, so that fixed it.  I am now passing _all_ of Blargg's MMC3 IRQ test ROMs.  But unfortunately, when I say all I really mean _all_ of them - including _both_ Rev A and Rev B tests (#5 and #6).  I don't think that's supposed to happen - in fact, I didn't even think it was possible.  Well...more debugging.  If anyone has any ideas let me know.
<br />
<br />But hey, I'm passing all of Blargg's tests! Progress!! <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />
